{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cedd43da4a","title":"民主选举论纲","origin":"北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"faf3200692","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"cedd43da4a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"25804569a0","name":"蒋兴仁"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4da2fab09b","type":"title","text":"民主选举论纲(以上几篇论点的总结)","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedd43da4a"},{"id":"cd5eb96b61","type":"authors","text":"北京大学蒋兴仁","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedd43da4a"},{"id":"da01d3398f","type":"paragraph","text":"（蒋兴仁：北京大学生物系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedd43da4a"},{"id":"cb87b9fe09","type":"paragraph","text":"一、民主选举论纲","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedd43da4a"},{"id":"c788dab9b2","type":"paragraph","text":"1．我国目前选举方式不民主。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedd43da4a"},{"id":"0a2b000c37","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)目前选举时大家对候选人不了解，介绍千篇一律“努力学习工作热心”，作风正派联系群众，投票只是在于相信党的提名的基础上实质上是指派。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedd43da4a"},{"id":"82a738161e","type":"paragraph","text":"(2)选民代表的广泛性只建立于出身的广泛性上如民主党派，青年妇女，忽视了个体差异是形式主义也是有职无权的根据。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedd43da4a"},{"id":"8787f850f1","type":"paragraph","text":"(3)代表虽经人民选举，但人民选举时既不了解他对各政策方针的态度，选举后又独立管理政权，所以不能保证代表人民有像前匈牙利波兰一样脱离人民的危险。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedd43da4a"},{"id":"1543293d0a","type":"paragraph","text":"(4)选举是人民管理政权的一个主要环节，而目前选举却像选模范一样，而且选出的代表也不是社会活动家，而多数是模范。他既不懂得怎样管理政治，又不代表人民，很容易受个别政治家的愚弄，因此领导一变质就有使政权变质的危险。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedd43da4a"},{"id":"0ef1d3217d","type":"appellation","text":"从上面几点看出我国选举方式是民主的形式独裁的内容。只当领导正确时才偶然合乎人民的意志，领导变质时随时有变成个人专政的危险如拉科西，格罗，斯大林事件就是最好的例子。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedd43da4a"},{"id":"ff3dd5eac2","type":"appellation","text":"2．民主选举方式的基本特征：","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedd43da4a"},{"id":"74e8bc5dad","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)竞选：选举前让愿参加候选的人都来竞选说明自己对○○○○问题的看法，被选出以后执行怎样的政策方针坚持○○○○○代表人民做些什么?选举人竞选也得发表竞选演说宣传○○○○种主要政治问题的观点。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedd43da4a"},{"id":"401dcc826a","type":"paragraph","text":"(2)辩论会和信任票：选举后必须经常向选民报告之后举行辩论会和讨论会，必要时投信任票。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedd43da4a"},{"id":"34cb1c8f10","type":"subtitle","text":"基层单位领导由选举产生：基层单位由本单位，○要人员通过竞选的方式以避免○○中的官僚主义(选举前国家可以调动)如教师选校长，工人选厂长。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedd43da4a"},{"id":"0950e272e5","type":"paragraph","text":"参考资料：","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedd43da4a"},{"id":"befac54d75","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)本人大字报","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedd43da4a"},{"id":"627745f2dd","type":"paragraph","text":"(2)中华人民共和国宪法","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedd43da4a"},{"id":"b1fb71254d","type":"paragraph","text":"(3)1937年最高苏维埃选举条件第六章。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedd43da4a"},{"id":"19a942fd13","type":"paragraph","text":"(4)斯大林：在莫斯科斯大林选民大会上的演说。(1937．12．11)","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedd43da4a"},{"id":"4ea5a9fd13","type":"paragraph","text":"(5)人民日报57年6月26日","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedd43da4a"},{"id":"1be511d86a","type":"appellation","text":"(6)中国青年报1957年6月20日惨痛的教训","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedd43da4a"},{"id":"fb9388d4c0","type":"appellation","text":"(7)辽宁日报","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedd43da4a"},{"id":"2c28adedb0","type":"appellation","text":"(8)周恩来政治报告","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedd43da4a"},{"id":"58ffdaf270","type":"paragraph","text":"(9)南斯拉夫资料汇编121—195，230—259。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedd43da4a"}],"page":{"id":"c193d22099","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cedd43da4a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}